item.title: Worldmed Assistance (Nepal) Pvt. Ltd
item.description: Worldmed provides a comprehensive, integrated, global assistance offering to support the medical, security and travel assistance needs of travellers, various companies and local nationals wherever they may be located around the country in Nepal. The service, available 24/7, provides a single point of contact to gain immediate access to expertise, advice and help on the ground.
